[telegram] <Caleb> Guys, the point of this stress test was not to make money. I didn’t win, and I spent the full 6 hours attempting to make swaps... 
The crypto space in general should not be a means of getting rich. The whole point is to restore the power of trade back to the people where it belongs. 
I’ve invested countless hours and energy into decentralized currencies, and thus far I have not actually made any money in terms of Fiat. I’m begging everyone involved to regain perspective and reevaluate why you’re here. Otherwise the opportunity we’ve been given to regain control of wealth will be gone.
